    <entry>
      <title>序列类型</title>
      <link href="/2022/050229345.html"/>
      <url>/2022/050229345.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="一、序列类型通用函数"><a href="#一、序列类型通用函数" class="headerlink" title="一、序列类型通用函数"></a>一、序列类型通用函数</h3><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python">len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回序列的长度min<span class="token punctuation">(</span>s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回序列的最小元素，s中元素需要可比较max<span class="token punctuation">(</span>s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回序列的最大元素，s中元素需要可比较s<span class="token punctuation">.</span>index<span class="token punctuation">(</span>i<span class="token punctuation">)</span>或s<span class="token punctuation">.</span>index<span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">,</span>i<span class="token punctuation">,</span>j<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回序列从i开始到j位置中x第一次出现的位置s<span class="token punctuation">.</span>count<span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回序列中s出现的总次数</code></pre><h3 id="二、元组类型"><a href="#二、元组类型" class="headerlink" title="二、元组类型"></a>二、元组类型</h3><p>1.元组是一种序列类型，一旦创建就不能修改</p><p>2.使用小括号()或tuple()创建，元素间用逗号分隔</p><p>3.使用时可以用也可以不用小括号()</p><h3 id="三、列表类型"><a href="#三、列表类型" class="headerlink" title="三、列表类型"></a>三、列表类型</h3><p>1.列表是一种序列类型，创建后可以随便修改</p><p>2.使用方括号[]或list()创建，元素间用逗号，分隔</p><p>3.列表中个元素类型可以不同，无长度限制</p><h4 id="列表类型操作函数和方法"><a href="#列表类型操作函数和方法" class="headerlink" title="列表类型操作函数和方法"></a>列表类型操作函数和方法</h4><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python">ls<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span>x<span class="token operator">//</span>替换列表ls底i元素为xls<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">:</span>j<span class="token punctuation">:</span>k<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">=</span>lt<span class="token operator">//</span>用列表lt替换ls切片后所对应元素子列表<span class="token keyword">del</span> ls<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">//</span>删除列表ls中第i元素<span class="token keyword">del</span> ls<span class="token punctuation">[</span>i<span class="token punctuation">:</span>j<span class="token punctuation">:</span>k<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">//</span>删除列表ls中第i到j以k为步长的元素ls<span class="token operator">+=</span>lt<span class="token operator">//</span>更新列表ls，将列表lt元素郑家到列表ls中ls<span class="token operator">*=</span>n<span class="token operator">//</span>更新列表，其元素重复n次ls<span class="token punctuation">.</span>append<span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>在列表ls最后增加一个元素xls<span class="token punctuation">,</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>删除列表ls中所有元素ls<span class="token punctuation">.</span>copy<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>生成一个新列表，赋值ls中所有元素ls<span class="token punctuation">.</span>insert<span class="token punctuation">(</span>i<span class="token punctuation">,</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>在列表ls中第i位置增加元素xls<span class="token punctuation">.</span>pop<span class="token punctuation">(</span>i<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>将列表ls中第i位置元素取出并删除该元素ls<span class="token punctuation">.</span>remove<span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>将列表ls中出现的第一个元素x删除ls<span class="token punctuation">.</span>reverse<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>将列表ls中的元素反转</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> python </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>基本统计</title>
      <link href="/2022/050245059.html"/>
      <url>/2022/050245059.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="一、基本统计值"><a href="#一、基本统计值" class="headerlink" title="一、基本统计值"></a>一、基本统计值</h3><p>1.总个数：len()</p><p>2.求和：for…in</p><p>3.平均值：求和&#x2F;总个数</p><p>4.方差：各数据与平均数差的平方的和的平均数</p><p>5.中位数：排序，然后… 奇数找中间一个，偶数找中间两个取平均</p><p>​sorted(x)函数为列表排序</p><h3 id="二、字典类型"><a href="#二、字典类型" class="headerlink" title="二、字典类型"></a>二、字典类型</h3><h4 id="字典类型是“映射”的体现"><a href="#字典类型是“映射”的体现" class="headerlink" title="字典类型是“映射”的体现"></a>字典类型是“映射”的体现</h4><p>1.键值对：键是对数据索引的拓展</p><p>2.字典是键值对的集合，键值对之间无序</p><p>3.采用大括号{}和dict()创建，键值对用冒号：表示</p><p>例如：</p><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token operator">&amp;</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#123;&lt;键1>:&lt;值1>, &lt;键2>:&lt;值2>, &lt;键3>:&lt;值3>&amp;#125;</span></code></pre><h4 id="字典类型操作函数和方法"><a href="#字典类型操作函数和方法" class="headerlink" title="字典类型操作函数和方法"></a>字典类型操作函数和方法</h4><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">del</span> d<span class="token punctuation">[</span>k<span class="token punctuation">]</span><span class="token operator">//</span>删除字典d中键k对应的数据值k <span class="token keyword">in</span> d<span class="token operator">//</span>判断键k是否在字典d中d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>keys<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回字典d中所有的键信息d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>values<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回字典d中所有的值信息d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>items<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回字典d中所有的键值对信息d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>get<span class="token punctuation">(</span>k<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>default<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>键k存在则返回相应值，不存在则返回<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>default<span class="token operator">></span>值d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>pop<span class="token punctuation">(</span>k<span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>default<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>键k存在则取出相应值，不存在则返回<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>default<span class="token operator">></span>值d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>popitem<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>随机从字典d中取出一个键值对，以元组形式返回d<span class="token punctuation">.</span>clear<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>删除所有的键值对len<span class="token punctuation">(</span>d<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>返回字典d中元素的个数</code></pre><h3 id="三、jieba库的使用"><a href="#三、jieba库的使用" class="headerlink" title="三、jieba库的使用"></a>三、jieba库的使用</h3><h4 id="简要介绍"><a href="#简要介绍" class="headerlink" title="简要介绍"></a>简要介绍</h4><ol><li><p>中文文本需要通过分词获得单个词语</p></li><li><p>jieba是优秀的中文分词第三方库，需要额外安装</p></li><li><p>jieba库提供三种分词模式，最简单只需掌握一个函数</p></li><li><p>（cmd命令行）pip install jieba</p></li><li><p>利用一个中文词库，确定汉字之间的关联概率</p></li><li><p>汉字之间概率大的组成词组，形成分词结果</p></li><li><p>除了分词，用户还可以添加自定义的词组</p></li></ol><h4 id="jieba分词的三种模式"><a href="#jieba分词的三种模式" class="headerlink" title="jieba分词的三种模式"></a>jieba分词的三种模式</h4><ol><li>精确模式：把文本精确的切分开</li><li>全模式：把文本中所有可能的词语都扫描出来，有冗余</li><li>搜索引擎模式：在精确模式基础上，对长词再次切分</li></ol><h4 id="jieba库常用函数"><a href="#jieba库常用函数" class="headerlink" title="jieba库常用函数"></a>jieba库常用函数</h4><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python">jieba<span class="token punctuation">,</span>lcut<span class="token punctuation">(</span>s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>精确模式，返回一个列表类型的分词结果jieba<span class="token punctuation">.</span>lcut<span class="token punctuation">(</span>s<span class="token punctuation">,</span>cut_all<span class="token operator">=</span>true<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>全模式，返回一个列表类型的分词结果，存在冗余jieba<span class="token punctuation">.</span>lcut_for_search<span class="token punctuation">(</span>s<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>搜索引擎模式，返回一个列表类型的分词结果，存在冗余jieba<span class="token punctuation">.</span>add_word<span class="token punctuation">(</span>w<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token operator">//</span>向分词词典增加新词w</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> python </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>库引用</title>
      <link href="/2022/042864875.html"/>
      <url>/2022/042864875.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="库引用"><a href="#库引用" class="headerlink" title="库引用"></a>库引用</h4><p>1.传统引用</p><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token operator">+</span> 库名调用：库名<span class="token punctuation">.</span>函数名<span class="token punctuation">(</span>参数<span class="token punctuation">)</span>例：<span class="token keyword">import</span> turtleturtle<span class="token punctuation">.</span>pensize<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre><p>2.使用from+保留字引用，调用时可以直接使用函数名（前提是没有别的函数与库中的函数重名）</p><pre><code>例如：from turtle import*pensize(123)</code></pre><p>3.取别名（由 import 和 as 保留字共同完成）</p><pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python">使用方式为：<span class="token keyword">import</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>库名<span class="token operator">></span> <span class="token keyword">as</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>库别名<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>库别名<span class="token operator">></span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token operator">&lt;</span>函数名<span class="token operator">></span>（<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>函数参数<span class="token operator">></span>）列：<span class="token keyword">import</span> turtle <span class="token keyword">as</span> tt<span class="token punctuation">.</span>pensize<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">123</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> python </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>python基本数据类型练习</title>
